Awesome clip Frank, that is clear as a bell.  I love the fact that they seem to know so much as to what is going on in our personal live, such as your pizza clip or Bruce's phone ringing clip.  As you take a step back and look at the bigger picture as to what the true means are regarding the clips, we can assume that they acknowledge us more than what we actually know.  By them comfirming facts here on this plane and what we are experiencing at that moment is hugh for our research.
   
  Just my thoughts!
   
  Juli

Frank Sumption <franks-boxes@...> wrote:
           They report on her. Barbara Simpson is a talk show host from San Francisco, she used to fill in for Art Bell eons ago. I used to get stuff on EVPmaker like 'Barbara Simpson--astral'. 
 
 There's alot more to ITC than getting a dead person's name, or some techno guide, it can be amazing if ya don't prejudge what's supposed to come thorugh, or block it by expectations. 
 
 
 Frank-S
